Package mst.prim

Class MemoryManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • mst.prim.MemoryManager

  • public class MemoryManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Manages allocation and deallocation of the arrays and priority queues that are big and allocated very often. Get methods have a parameter size that denotes the recommended size of the object. Methods free are used to free the object.
